{"tid":1478850,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連登無人吹風向, 唔好自己分化自己","createTime":"2019-08-16T16:22:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T16:41:18.000Z","uid":56546,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8f60d77ff57c8017609029aa62db7154e1cc4fc8","tid":1478850,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:22:25.000Z","msg":"有幾個post話關口有一班疑似老解人員帶曬gear過關<br />\n係咁俾人話散播白色恐怖等人唔敢出<br />\n跟住又一個post 話無fc一定流料<br />\n中共都未出手<br />\n我地自己已經散曬<br />\n<br />\n其實你地唔使理成件事真定假<br />\n總之只需知道中共已經準備安插大量嘅鬼入黎<br />\n係比平時多十幾倍<br />\n心中有個防範就夠<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n提你地嘅真係出於好心<br />\n唔信同質疑嘅, 有判斷能力都係啱<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過大家嘅大方向係<br />\n既然人地派多十倍人<br />\n我地更加應該出黎同佢地對衡<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">818 見</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"144f9d938c42a4ffd512aa13f256c0d007c002f5","tid":1478850,"uid":88263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:23:12.000Z","msg":"快啲嚟啦，攬炒啦<br />\n<br />\n[寧鳴而死！]All in 攬炒好似係唯一嘅出路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1476343\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1476343</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"78e79dd14c42e80903113e29863682ab94ef97b1","tid":1478850,"uid":212217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:23:31.000Z","msg":"<strong>和理非係時候要進化喇! 818 同步搞! 後備持久戰plan! </strong><br />\n<br />\n［推上熱門！！！］全港新戰略‐和理非『節奏抗爭』每日9點準時敲擊!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475606\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475606</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/36uybaW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F36uybaW.jpg&h=ddfac6a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a42c1d8a4138509f6f811e55b580e0594629b397","tid":1478850,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:26:52.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"264581c0594ed85154eecf39882f225c975ab8d8","tid":1478850,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,